{
  "stem": "7598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so for about 18 months, we were able to conduct some sort of correspondence via New York because America didn't enter the war until [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] December of '41, I think, and by which time we had, we had left.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the beginning, we went back to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans were very systematic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, I am being objective about it because so much time has gone by.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember the curfew and being frightened and very concerned, not knowing what was going to come next.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But I can understand them organizing everything slowly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, I understand they never told the people they were going to be gassed, because they didn't want any rebellion.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wanted people to do as they were told.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The curfew was established quite early on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't always stick to it, because I was a girl of 13.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My brother was tall for 15, and we, we knew that young Jews were being surrounded for any excuse to go to, to work camps.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he, you know, kept a low profile.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we went back to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my uncle and aunt were in their own home, and so they had their own clothes and, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But my brother and I didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Our school books were in our apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was decided they would have a go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to the [NON-ENGLISH], which was the headquarters of the Gestapo, and asked for permission to go into my apartment.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And strangely enough, they gave it to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they said it was-- I was the only one that would be allowed to go in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother wouldn't, nor would my aunt.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
